<exercise id="fs-idm39063008">
<problem id="fs-idm134639376">
<para id="fs-idm77899792">Flokkaðu hvert efni í töflunni sem annaðhvort málm, jónaefni, sameindaefni eða samgilt net:<newline/> [[TABLE:fs-idp139392608]]</para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-idm12335424">
<para id="fs-idm45120288">X = jónaefni; Y = málmur; Z = samgilt net</para>
</solution>
</exercise>
